```kotlin
interface CallRepository : JpaRepository<CallEntity, String> {
    fun findByInitiatorUserId(userId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByRecipientUserId(userId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByInitiatorUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByRecipientUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): List<CallEntity>
    fun findActiveCallByUserId(userId: String): CallEntity?  // 진행중인 통화
}
```

#### 2.3 Service 계층

**CallService.kt** - 핵심 비즈니스 로직
```kotlin
@Service
class CallService(
    private val callRepository: CallRepository,
    private val callStatisticsRepository: CallStatisticsRepository,
) {
    @Transactional
    fun initiateCall(initiatorId: String, recipientId: String): CallEntity

    @Transactional
    fun acceptCall(callId: String, recipientId: String): CallEntity

    @Transactional
    fun rejectCall(callId: String, recipientId: String): String

    @Transactional
    fun endCall(callId: String, userId: String): CallEntity

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getCallById(callId: String): CallEntity

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getUserCallHistory(userId: String, limit: Int = 20): List<CallEntity>

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getActiveCall(userId: String): CallEntity?
}
```

**CallMatchingService.kt** - 매칭 알고리즘
```kotlin
@Service
class CallMatchingService(
    private val callRepository: CallRepository,
